'''芭芭拉·德米克'''（{{lang-en|'''Babara Demick'''}}），[[美國|美國]]女記者，曾任《[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]》[[北京|北京]]分社社長、[[首尔|首尔]]分社社長。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://articles.latimes.com/writers/barbara-demick |title=''Los Angeles Times'' |access-date=2014-12-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090425192242/http://articles.latimes.com/writers/barbara-demick |archive-date=2009-04-25 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

芭芭拉·德米克關注並廣泛報導[[朝鮮民主主義人民共和國|朝鮮民主主義人民共和國]]的[[朝鮮民主主義人民共和國經濟|經濟社會發展]]及[[朝鮮民主主義人民共和國人權|人權狀況]]。曾撰寫一系列關於[[清津市|清津市]]內[[北韓人|北韓人]]生活的報導。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=4728349 |title=Reporter Gets Rare Glimpse at North Korea, National Public Radio, July 3, 2005. |access-date=2014-12-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150509141352/http://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=4728349 |archive-date=2015-05-09 |dead-url=no }}</ref>2010年，芭芭拉·德米克憑藉其北韓題材[[報導文學|報導文學]]《[[我們最幸福：北韓人民的真實生活|我們最幸福：北韓人民的真實生活]]》獲得[[塞繆爾·約翰遜獎|塞繆爾·約翰遜獎]]。<ref>{{cite news |title=Journalist Barbara Demick wins non-fiction prize with tale of life in North Korea |url=http://www.thisislondon.co.uk/standard/article-23851888-journalist-barbara-demick-wins-non-fiction-prize-with-tale-of-life-in-north-korea.do |accessdate=2010-07-02 |newspaper=London Evening Standard |date=2010-07-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100705130137/http://www.thisislondon.co.uk/standard/article-23851888-journalist-barbara-demick-wins-non-fiction-prize-with-tale-of-life-in-north-korea.do |archive-date=2010-07-05 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2020年，芭芭拉·德米克的新书《吃佛》出版，聚焦于[[中華人民共和國|中国]][[四川省|四川省]][[阿坝县|阿坝县]]的藏族人生活。<ref>{{cite web |title=噬佛：從一座城市，窺見西藏的劫難與求生 |url=https://activity.books.com.tw/crosscat/show/A00000016991?loc=P_0033_001 |website=博客来 |accessdate=2020-07-21|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200721025444/https://activity.books.com.tw/crosscat/show/A00000016991?loc=P_0033_001|archivedate=2020-07-21}}</ref>

